Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.44,0:00:30.21,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,A TOHO - O.B. PLANNlNG\NPRODUCTlON
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.88,0:00:38.18,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Based on Tetsu Adachi's\N"Weather Report Girl"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.94,0:01:03.91,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe the old guy tried it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.94,0:01:05.91,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You're serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.95,0:01:08.94,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Where does he get off\Nthinking he can pull that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.62,0:01:15.95,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, just for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.99,0:01:20.62,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I set up that meeting\Nwith the agency! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.63,0:01:25.62,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!\NYou tryin' to make a fool of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.97,0:01:32.63,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I said no!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.28,0:01:43.15,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch it.\NDon't be so full of yourself, Keiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.99,0:01:50.25,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Because she...\NSHE is coming back from France.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.29,0:01:52.99,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Your reign is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.03,0:01:54.99,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Keiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.66,0:01:57.32,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,"She?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.24,0:02:07.57,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,WEATHER REPORT GIRL 2
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.01,0:02:09.34,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori Shimamori?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.38,0:02:13.64,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. She's been working\Nin France for the last two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.68,0:02:18.64,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,As a demotion, right?\NDid she get in trouble with a guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.69,0:02:23.09,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.\NShe isn't a tramp like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.32,0:02:25.26,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Well excuse me for being a tramp!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.29,0:02:27.02,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Look. Look. I'm a tramp.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:32.39,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,She's from a rich family.\NDad's a member of the Diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.70,0:02:36.00,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,So, she's just a\Ngirl with connections.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.04,0:02:39.34,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Me! Me! I'll take it to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.37,0:02:42.21,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell!\NI'm giving this to Kaori!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.38,0:02:47.01,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,A man would be proud\Nto get a job offer so soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.05,0:02:49.35,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Japan's changed, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.38,0:02:53.28,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the latest from Paris?\NYou're even more beautiful now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.69,0:02:55.02,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.06,0:02:56.75,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:03:02.19,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Merci. I'm overjoyed to\Nget such a warm reception.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.36,0:03:05.16,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you can still speak Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.67,0:03:08.69,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Japan's number one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.74,0:03:10.40,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,'Scuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.34,0:03:16.07,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Keiko Nakadai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.24,0:03:21.30,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're the infamous\NWeather Report Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:24.78,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori Shimamori.\NHow do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.09,0:03:26.71,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a cool one, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.75,0:03:29.75,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Just 'cuz your\Ndaddy's such a big shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:32.35,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You've had it so easy growing up...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.39,0:03:35.73,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,...you can't believe anyone\Nwould ever be your enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.76,0:03:37.42,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You little punk bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.13,0:03:45.00,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a regular\Nemployee making a living.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.04,0:03:48.41,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go saying I use\Nmy father's influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.44,0:03:51.07,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to have\Nanything to do with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.11,0:03:54.44,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit talking tough, bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.75,0:03:57.65,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Things have changed\Nwhile you've been gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.78,0:04:01.58,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm running things in\Nthis TV studio now!.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.43,0:04:08.76,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,My, such mighty words\Nfrom a weather girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.80,0:04:12.46,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you heard?\NThe news anchor's a bit more important.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.47,0:04:16.26,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,No more tits and ass shows.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.30,0:04:19.76,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on we're going\Nto have a decent news show...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.81,0:04:22.50,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,...with Kaori here the lead anchor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.44,0:04:28.47,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You can keep doing your\Nstrip show, if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.82,0:04:38.59,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it.\NPut her in her place!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.50,0:04:45.69,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.33,0:04:49.82,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:53.50,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:57.27,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I challenge you to\Na duel! To the death!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.85,0:05:02.14,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Lemme go!\NTo the death, I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.18,0:05:03.51,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Keiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.46,0:05:12.52,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Keiko! Keiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.86,0:05:16.16,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?\NShe's on soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.20,0:05:19.17,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I know she's in there,\Nbut she won't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:25.20,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:27.87,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you can't just go in!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.91,0:05:31.54,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. Keiko, we're coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.82,0:05:42.88,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Keiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:48.22,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.93,0:05:53.56,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.54,0:05:58.50,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.\NNo underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:06:00.56,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,And when the light hits it,\Nthe show really begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.45,0:06:15.42,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,So, does this get\Na rise out of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.26,0:06:20.89,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,NEWSCASTER 9
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.23,0:06:32.90,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, everyone. Tonight we begin\Na new series: Newscaster 9.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.94,0:06:35.87,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your main anchor,\NKaori Shimamori.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.62,0:06:50.61,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,P.M. Murakami said he'd call\Nan immediate meeting with...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.66,0:06:53.63,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,...the other ministers to discuss\Neffective countermeasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.66,0:06:55.63,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,They reached a\Nmutual agreement and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.97,0:07:03.27,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You sit there, reading\Nyour teleprompter script...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.30,0:07:05.93,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I get to show up any\Nway I damn well please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:08.93,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead. I'm ready for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.98,0:07:10.90,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, everybody! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.91,0:07:11.90,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Diagram
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.01,0:07:14.81,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Drastic action is expected\Nto improve the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.92,0:07:17.97,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,We have something just in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:21.78,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,At the Japanese embassy\Nin Nigeria early this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.62,0:07:27.25,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, raise this thing!\NIt's stuffy in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.96,0:07:36.99,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, move it!\NThis thing weighs a ton!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.07,0:07:44.67,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,That report from Nigeria has\Ncaused a change in our schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:48.67,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait anymore!\NMaybe if I started a fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.02,0:07:56.01,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!\NHere we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:07:59.42,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.64,0:08:13.04,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Night!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.07,0:08:16.30,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,The mike isn't there.\NGet off the cord!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.71,0:08:18.54,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.05,0:08:22.34,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. We thought\Nwe could make it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.38,0:08:24.41,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,The news report ran over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.99,0:08:32.05,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, that... THAT...!!\NShe stole my spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:41.27,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I had to wait down in that little\Nhole in this getup for an hour!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.74,0:08:46.20,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not training to be a magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.74,0:08:51.73,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,This was a once in a lifetime chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:08:58.17,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You...!!! I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.72,0:09:02.71,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasted time on that Nigeria\Nreport and killed the schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.76,0:09:05.42,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't handle it as\Nwell as I could have.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.03,0:09:12.73,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides that, I was disorganized\Nand ended up throwing everyone off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.77,0:09:14.43,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.10,0:09:19.06,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, people. Move it!\NWe're on battle stations tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.11,0:09:21.40,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Get some people over\Nto the Foreign Ministry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:23.91,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,The press conference is at 11:00.\NGet all the facts, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:32.38,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Bet there were a lot of\Ncalls about Newscaster 9 tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:34.98,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. The lines\Nwere jammed before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.02,0:09:37.72,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,They started ringing as\Nsoon as the newscast began.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:39.42,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as it began?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.46,0:09:42.39,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,The reaction to Kaori\Nhas been outstanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.43,0:09:44.12,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,We had our hands full.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:47.80,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.\NAre they still ringing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:50.70,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. There've been\Nabout 400 calls so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.74,0:09:53.76,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! How many were\Ncomplaints about me not going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.81,0:09:56.10,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Ummm... None, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.14,0:09:58.44,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.48,0:10:00.97,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Not one?! Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.18,0:10:04.45,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, enjoy yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.48,0:10:08.01,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You get your kicks out of\Nfeeling superior to other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:12.12,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all just employees.\NThe employees make the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.12,0:10:16.72,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all just employees.\NThe employees make the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.76,0:10:20.76,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Popularity like yours is\Na fleeting thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:23.77,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll you do when you're thirty?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.80,0:10:25.74,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Get married and quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.84,0:10:29.03,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a disgustingly\Nboring woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.08,0:10:31.84,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,But apparently more\Npopular than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:01.17,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,She wasn't on...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.21,0:11:04.54,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Keiko wasn't on TV last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.82,0:11:11.51,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.55,0:11:13.21,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.22,0:11:20.22,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Kei... Keiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.19,0:11:22.75,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yamagishi.\NGood morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.80,0:11:25.46,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you dressed like...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.50,0:11:27.90,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm acting like a new girl should.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.17,0:11:32.54,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know that.\NShe's still new here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.57,0:11:35.20,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Keiko, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.24,0:11:37.87,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't try to\Nrise above the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.81,0:11:41.54,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be an idol forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.58,0:11:44.57,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't let the fickle\Naudience lead me astray.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.23,0:11:59.86,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! I don't want\Nto see you like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:05.60,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Keiko Nakadai! You are the\Nalmighty Weather Report Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.28,0:12:11.84,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, aren't we looking\Nmodest these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:15.58,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm through playing your games!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.62,0:12:17.78,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Just lemme have you, bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.92,0:12:22.29,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do whatever I want to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:24.95,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Director's privilege!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.19,0:12:31.63,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Get her! Get her!\NChoke the life outta her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.34,0:12:39.93,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,If I was dead I wouldn't\Neven let you lick me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.97,0:12:42.63,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna do?\NQuit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.68,0:12:49.64,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Piss off! I'll get back to where\NI was even if I have to crawl!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.66,0:13:01.35,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:08.23,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Chairman!\NYou're out of the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.27,0:13:11.90,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be\Nlaying in some sickbed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.94,0:13:15.27,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you done to\Nour gold mine, you idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:17.24,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold mine?\NMr. President!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.86,0:13:33.59,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,What is all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.76,0:13:38.73,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,The floor couldn't hold\Nall the letters protesting...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.76,0:13:40.93,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,...Keiko not being on last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.97,0:13:43.66,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,But no one called in about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.70,0:13:48.66,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Because your fans\Nwere jamming up the lines!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.71,0:13:52.41,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Shimamori, if you bump\Nthe weather report again...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.45,0:13:55.18,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,...a full-scale riot may\Nbreak out! Remember that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.38,0:13:58.25,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.28,0:14:00.91,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Keiko's disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.95,0:14:03.39,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't think she fell\Nwith the mail, do you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:21.06,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:38.96,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.99,0:14:40.00,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm wet, it's only\Nbecause of the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.03,0:14:43.76,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I even believe it'd\Nturn out any differently?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.06,0:14:52.10,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I can't sleep,\Nthat's because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.77,0:14:58.44,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Everywhere I go, people\Njust seem to irritate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.41,0:15:07.38,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,So all I do is just take a\Ndeep breath and try to go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.42,0:15:15.05,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,A woman's heart is like the\Nchanging weather, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.09,0:15:21.43,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,And a kiss like that isn't\Nenough to set it ablaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.47,0:15:24.80,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,After the rain stops, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.77,0:15:28.47,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get our hearts racing along.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.48,0:15:36.44,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,When it clears up,\Nwe'll love like it's paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.48,0:15:40.78,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,After the rain stops, let's go...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.82,0:15:44.95,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, Newscaster 9\Nis beating all other news shows
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.99,0:15:49.83,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,With its 30% share,\Nthe program is unmatched
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.46,0:15:52.45,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.50,0:15:55.49,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Our ratings data this\Nmonth shows all our programs..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.53,0:15:58.77,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,...outside of Newscaster 9\Nare getting clobbered
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:16:02.60,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Keiko and Kaori are\Nthe prized boxed melons...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.64,0:16:06.24,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,...in a store full of rotten fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.86,0:16:18.48,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth,\Nour Goddesses of Fortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:29.47,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,These two will become\Nthe new face of ATV!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.50,0:16:32.77,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have a huge promotion\Ncampaign to enhance our image.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.17,0:16:36.51,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do what I can to help\Nus through this crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.54,0:16:39.20,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like working with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.55,0:16:46.78,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,But we're all in the same boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.43,0:17:02.73,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's get a picture\Nfor the company newsletter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.20,0:17:06.17,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, you can keep\Nyour clothes on for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.57,0:17:09.47,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you two.\NShoulders together. Smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:11.74,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,As slutty as usual, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.58,0:17:19.57,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do what it takes to prove\NI'm number one here at ATV.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.09,0:17:23.82,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Flashing your tits won't\Nkeep you popular forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.19,0:17:28.15,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll think like that\Nwhen I'm as old as you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.19,0:17:30.72,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,If your career lasts that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.20,0:17:38.66,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,At least my figure will last\Nlonger than yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:55.58,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, have this and\Nthis ready for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.96,0:17:59.55,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko, we're running late.\NLet's get to the rehearsal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.59,0:18:00.96,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:10.53,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,"Climb Mt. Niitaka"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.64,0:18:14.63,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,She's calling...\NShe's calling for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.64,0:18:18.30,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko! The rehearsal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.32,0:18:30.81,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't find this belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.66,0:18:34.32,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Figured you'd know where it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.16,0:18:37.63,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,But I found it anyway, so it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.66,0:18:39.65,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,For that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.97,0:18:42.96,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't working\Nor anything, were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:45.13,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.17,0:18:47.57,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just some stupid\Nvoice-over stuff, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.61,0:18:49.51,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You could blow that off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.28,0:18:52.27,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.31,0:18:55.34,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,And who got me kicked\Ninto that stupid job?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:18:59.61,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're here, why\Ndon't you clean up this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.65,0:19:01.92,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and the laundry needs to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.36,0:19:06.29,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I'll try to keep on top of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.33,0:19:07.85,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Harpy! Hellspawn bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.91,0:19:24.27,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, old timer?\NYou look blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:27.04,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Shimamori.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:33.22,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really just doing\Nthe morning radio show now?.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.72,0:19:36.35,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,And some voice-overs, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.39,0:19:39.19,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing that gets your\Nface on the screen, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.22,0:19:42.63,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Things didn't work out\Nbeing the old weather girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:45.89,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. That's a job for young girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:48.72,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Like Keiko Nakadai?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.60,0:19:55.73,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's time Keiko took a fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:14.39,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something about\Na really nice restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.43,0:20:16.76,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the air seems different.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.80,0:20:20.06,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,If the PR staff hadn't let us come...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.10,0:20:23.09,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,...I doubt we'd ever have seen\None of these from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.31,0:20:33.77,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Presenting Miss Kaori Shimamura\Nand Miss Keiko Nakadai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.85,0:20:38.21,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Keiko... She's lovely...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.42,0:20:41.39,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get some good pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.42,0:20:45.05,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,This is for the train station\Nand in-car ad posters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:47.79,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's work together for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.43,0:20:52.80,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather sleazy dress, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.07,0:20:54.46,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.13,0:20:57.43,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three, four, five,\Nsix, seven, eight, nine, ten!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.47,0:21:00.80,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I won! I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.32,0:21:21.49,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,The wine list, Madame.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.43,0:21:26.33,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know about\Nwines, Miss Nakadai?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.37,0:21:27.39,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,A bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.43,0:21:30.40,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Then choose for us, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.48,0:21:40.17,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid women. Do they even\Nknow the right wines for a meal?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.78,0:21:46.15,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,The choice of wine in\NFrench cuisine reveals...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.19,0:21:50.85,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,character intelligence, and education.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.49,0:21:57.45,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori must have learned\Nit in France, but had Keiko do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.50,0:22:01.87,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Kaori's direct challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.90,0:22:04.70,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Keiko's in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.87,0:22:08.84,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be having saute\Nof fresh foie gras...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.87,0:22:10.84,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Valencia oranges\Nfor dessert, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.88,0:22:11.84,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.88,0:22:16.84,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then... A Bordeaux.\NChateau Lafite Rothschild.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.88,0:22:19.18,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,What year?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.22,0:22:21.55,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a '59?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.56,0:22:26.18,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,A magnificent order, Madame!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.23,0:22:30.22,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, I misjudged you.\NI'll fetch it at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.91,0:22:43.20,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,They call it a perfume for drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.24,0:22:46.87,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Its rich, mellow bouquet makes it\Nlike something from another world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.91,0:22:50.14,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I caresses the tongue like a\Nrainbow over heaven's rose garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.18,0:22:52.48,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,And its beauty...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.52,0:22:55.49,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides that, 1959\Nis considered to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.52,0:22:58.15,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,...one of the finest vintage years of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.92,0:23:03.22,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,And this wine has been\Nripening for nearly fifty years!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.26,0:23:06.49,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,It cannot be called a\Nmere wine at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.53,0:23:09.93,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,No! This is a gift\Nfrom the gods themselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.28,0:23:22.27,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!\NYou fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.62,0:23:25.85,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't some sports drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.88,0:23:29.62,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to take a sip and\Nroll it around on your tongue!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.96,0:23:33.95,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,As gently as you might\Nsuck the breast of a virgin.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.56,0:23:38.96,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I've just given\Naway my innocent daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.30,0:23:44.96,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,...and watched her get raped\Non her honeymoon night!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.31,0:23:53.07,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Keiko, cut it out!\NThis is business!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.15,0:23:56.55,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! Keiko,\Nwhat are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.32,0:24:02.98,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.66,0:24:07.32,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.99,0:24:09.98,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,'Scuse me, miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.33,0:24:13.86,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.33,0:24:18.33,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! All right! All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.41,0:25:33.04,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.08,0:25:34.38,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.41,0:25:35.38,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.41,0:25:36.44,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.02,0:25:39.75,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the new poster?\NJesus Christ...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.76,0:25:50.52,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,"Conquering the land,\Ngiving head to the age..."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.43,0:25:57.43,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.70,0:26:01.43,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,NO-O-O-O-O-O-O!!!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.41,0:26:09.44,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You have access to her apartment?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.78,0:26:15.12,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I've been having\Nyou take such close care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.02,0:26:19.12,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? What sort of\Nman does she see?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.43,0:26:22.69,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think she sees one.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.73,0:26:26.36,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.40,0:26:30.77,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,A shameless tramp like\Nher MUST see a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.80,0:26:33.24,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no sign of one!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.48,0:26:42.47,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,What are...?\NListening devices.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.51,0:26:46.38,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Keiko's going to be at a\Nstaff meeting tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.42,0:26:50.58,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,While she's gone, I want you\Nto plant these in her apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.19,0:26:58.09,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,If she should suddenly head\Nback, I'll warn you with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.13,0:27:00.79,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the operation and pull out!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.83,0:27:05.13,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,She seems to have a sixth\Nsense about any threats to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.17,0:27:07.43,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.47,0:27:08.70,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.75,0:27:23.69,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, the authorities\Nordered us to pull these posters.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.19,0:27:26.16,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a surprise?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.19,0:27:28.52,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,And it was a good shot of me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.56,0:28:07.53,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Nakadai?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.57,0:28:11.83,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't had lunch yet.\NWant to come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.87,0:28:15.20,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Well, what brings on\Nthis change in the forecast?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.24,0:28:17.21,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You inviting me to lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.24,0:28:20.91,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we should\Nwork a few things out.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.61,0:28:24.24,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Like ideas for the new posters.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.27,0:28:48.26,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.35,0:28:57.28,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,"Red Hot Burgers"
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.20,0:29:18.64,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.58,0:29:25.27,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.31,0:29:29.27,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kaori! I'm all set.\NWhere are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.31,0:29:32.28,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be having\Nlunch with Keiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.32,0:29:35.65,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm calling from the\Nlobby of her apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.69,0:29:40.28,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the lobby!\NOf course she's with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.33,0:29:44.63,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I may be a little late,\Nso tell the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.66,0:29:46.65,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk to you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.24,0:30:00.01,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I turned off the\NAC and left right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.65,0:30:03.90,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Why was my apartment so cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.92,0:30:07.35,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone must have been in\Nthere using the air conditioning...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.39,0:30:09.62,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,...while I was out.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.65,0:30:11.92,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,And the only person who\Ncould have done that...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.99,0:30:17.36,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!. It wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.96,0:30:19.66,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lie to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.70,0:30:23.10,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me what you did!\NConfess!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.01,0:30:30.34,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing her, she WOULD do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.38,0:30:34.37,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,She has a wild animal's\Nsense of self preservation.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.96,0:30:51.02,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.06,0:30:53.36,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?\NDid I tell you to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.40,0:30:55.70,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You went in early today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.73,0:30:59.00,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured you didn't\Nhave time to clean up.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.04,0:31:01.37,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you have good timing.\NWe have a guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.41,0:31:03.07,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi there.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.74,0:31:06.37,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Make something for us.\NYou can have these.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.41,0:31:09.07,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Your cooking's better, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.75,0:31:11.38,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fix it in a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.42,0:31:14.28,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Imagine, lunch for\NATV's biggest stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.32,0:31:16.41,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better do a good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.43,0:31:23.39,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you've trained her well.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.43,0:31:25.69,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though she\Nwas once your superior.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.73,0:31:27.70,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You can borrow her if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.73,0:31:31.73,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank you! Why don't we begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.77,0:31:33.10,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.45,0:31:52.12,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, bring on your boyfriends, Keiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.47,0:32:02.13,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.10,0:32:05.73,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Great! Craps out on\Nme just when I need it!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.51,0:32:51.18,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,There! There! Oh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.08,0:32:54.81,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.42,0:32:58.72,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,She knows!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.54,0:33:12.63,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad, Kaori!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.54,0:33:17.53,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You can buy bug detectors easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.58,0:33:21.10,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,This is high-tech Japan,\Nnot France, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.18,0:33:24.21,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Buy some quality\Nequipment next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.05,0:33:28.88,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you, "Made in Japan!"
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.21,0:33:55.54,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,First the bugs,\Nnow you're following me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.58,0:33:58.55,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,How unexpectedly low-class.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.58,0:34:01.58,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm through fooling around.\NI challenge you, Keiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.62,0:34:04.52,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time someone\Nbloodied your nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.19,0:34:09.18,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,How about one pool lap?\NA 100 meter freestyle race.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.23,0:34:11.25,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Think you'll win?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.20,0:34:16.60,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the best one on my\Nhigh school swim team.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.47,0:34:19.27,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiddy pool stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.25,0:34:32.55,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Set!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.58,0:34:33.64,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.64,0:34:53.16,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,The flower suit girl's fast!\NShe's gonna win!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.28,0:35:01.30,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheater! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.37,0:35:28.34,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.36,0:35:50.29,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I won! I am the winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.03,0:35:52.36,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.90,0:35:55.96,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a damned shame, those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.00,0:36:00.16,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Two gorgeous women, fighting.\NWho wants to see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.76,0:36:54.28,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Powerful! Vivacious!\NAnd elegant, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.69,0:36:56.72,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! They're great!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.10,0:37:04.76,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,And the finish!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.08,0:37:17.05,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You watched the Olympics last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.08,0:37:19.11,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,As did you, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.13,0:37:36.10,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in, Michiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.13,0:37:39.10,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to discuss\Nthings with Keiko again.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.14,0:37:40.47,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.41,0:37:46.48,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,How boring. Look what they've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.48,0:37:49.28,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,"People of the World, Believe in Tomorrow."\NHow boring. Look what they've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.28,0:37:50.91,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,"People of the World, Believe in Tomorrow."\NI liked the old one better.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.45,0:37:55.11,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't you be\Nembarrassed if your parents saw it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.15,0:37:58.78,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You should stop thinking\Nlike an ordinary person.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.82,0:38:00.69,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I AM an ordinary woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.49,0:38:04.83,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.16,0:38:10.07,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Your beauty hides\Nsomething far more extreme.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.00,0:38:14.84,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Something not easily\Nbrought to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.44,0:38:18.84,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,When you realize that,\Nyou'll be changed forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.18,0:38:21.17,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be a totally new person.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.82,0:38:29.38,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I envy you, Keiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.42,0:38:32.45,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,She cleans, does your wash.\NEverything!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.49,0:38:36.26,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally.\NShe even licks my panties clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.46,0:38:38.76,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.80,0:38:41.79,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, she washes\Nthem properly after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.83,0:38:43.82,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Stain removal, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.87,0:38:47.46,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she's making that up.\NRight, Keiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.51,0:38:51.34,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You cleaned these before.\NLook, Michiko. See?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.88,0:38:53.21,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.25,0:38:56.44,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.48,0:38:58.38,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Keiko, stop it...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.89,0:39:07.65,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Keiko, not when there's\Nsomeone else here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.86,0:39:10.85,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so uppity!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.90,0:39:13.80,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,And why are you the only\None who's fully dressed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.83,0:39:15.82,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Undress! All the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.94,0:39:25.47,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.62,0:40:06.28,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.92,0:40:11.62,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori... When did I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.26,0:40:13.59,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You're one to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.62,0:40:16.89,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen a strip\Nor S&M show that good.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.03,0:40:19.43,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Keiko's extreme, but you're\Nsomething else altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.46,0:40:21.12,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.47,0:40:24.30,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I got embarrassed just watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.34,0:40:25.96,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.34,0:40:29.77,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,But, it did excite me a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.94,0:40:34.97,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko, Keiko's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.25,0:40:39.51,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.92,0:40:49.45,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Do to me what you did for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.59,0:40:52.93,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,It's... Keiko's face!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.06,0:42:00.69,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it love or just infatuation?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.73,0:42:04.36,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need that\Nkind of talk from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.40,0:42:07.40,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but this whole\Nthing isn't fun anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.44,0:42:11.60,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,See you again.\NYeah, in a hundred years!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.68,0:42:15.08,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,The burning I feel in my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.11,0:42:18.41,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,...burns for lots more guys than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.72,0:42:22.05,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,When you burn for her,\Nbut she's not there for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.09,0:42:25.72,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,...is when a girl seems\Nto shine brighter still!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.76,0:42:32.42,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I take my time as\NI strip off my clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.03,0:42:40.27,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Shining bright in just my naked skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.11,0:42:48.10,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,On a passion-filled vacation,\NI don't want this to ever end.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.11,0:42:55.42,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this dazzling sky,\NI wanna hold it close to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.45,0:43:02.79,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,On a passion-filled vacation,\Nin a fire we build on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.46,0:43:10.13,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Burning on and on, wherever we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.83,0:43:44.17,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,On a passion-filled vacation,\NI wanna reach up and embrace the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.14,0:43:51.17,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna be free and\Nlet my passions ignite.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.21,0:43:58.51,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,On a passion-filled vacation,\NI'll let my troubles sleep it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.18,0:44:06.52,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,As I stand alone\Nin the flowing breeze.
